(ns ui.events
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [ajax.core :as ajax]
            [ui.db :as db]))

;; Initialize app DB
(rf/reg-event-db
 ::initialize-db
 (fn [_ _]
   db/default-db))

;; Navigation
(rf/reg-event-db
 ::set-active-panel
 (fn [db [_ panel-id]]
   (assoc db :active-panel panel-id)))

;; Loading state
(rf/reg-event-db
 ::set-loading
 (fn [db [_ loading?]]
   (assoc db :loading loading?)))

;; Fetch account summary data
(rf/reg-event-fx
 ::fetch-account-summary
 (fn [{:keys [db]} _]
   {:db (assoc db :loading true)
    :http-xhrio {:method :get
                 :uri "/api/account-summary"
                 :response-format (ajax/json-response-format {:keywords? true})
                 :on-success [::fetch-account-summary-success]
                 :on-failure [::fetch-account-summary-failure]}}))

(rf/reg-event-db
 ::fetch-account-summary-success
 (fn [db [_ response]]
   (-> db
       (assoc :account-summary response)
       (assoc :loading false))))

(rf/reg-event-db
 ::fetch-account-summary-failure
 (fn [db [_ response]]
   (-> db
       (assoc :error (:status-text response))
       (assoc :loading false))))

;; Fetch instrument performance
(rf/reg-event-fx
 ::fetch-instrument-performance
 (fn [{:keys [db]} [_ instrument]]
   {:db (assoc db :loading true)
    :http-xhrio {:method :get
                 :uri (str "/api/instrument-performance/" instrument)
                 :response-format (ajax/json-response-format {:keywords? true})
                 :on-success [::fetch-instrument-performance-success]
                 :on-failure [::fetch-instrument-performance-failure]}}))

(rf/reg-event-db
 ::fetch-instrument-performance-success
 (fn [db [_ response]]
   (-> db
       (assoc-in [:instrument-performance (:instrument response)] response)
       (assoc :loading false))))

(rf/reg-event-db
 ::fetch-instrument-performance-failure
 (fn [db [_ response]]
   (-> db
       (assoc :error (:status-text response))
       (assoc :loading false))))
